                                        <p>Changes made on this page will make system-wide changes.</p>
                                        <p></p>                                                                        
                                        <table class="table table-striped">
                                            <thead>
                                              <tr>
                                                <th scope="col">Area</th>
                                                <th scope="col">Setting</th>
                                                <th scope="col">Details</th>
                                                <th scope="col">Toggle</th>                                               
                                              </tr>
                                            </thead>
                                            <tbody>
                                              <tr>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>System</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Disable user registration</p></th>
                                                <td>The disable user registration option removes the ability for users to sign up manually. This removes the signup button from the home screen and only allows login to users who are in the system. This is typically turned off if you would like to pre-add your users through the bulk uploader or individual user facilities.</td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <label>
                                                        <input type="checkbox" data-toggle="toggle"> </label>                                                                                                             
                                                </td>
                                               </tr>       
                                               <tr>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>System</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>University address settings</p></th>
                                                <td>This is a mandatory setting. Typically, the invoice address.</td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".bd-example-modal-lg">Modify</button>                                                                                                     
                                                </td>
                                               </tr>       
                                               <tr>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>System</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Text and terminology</p></th>
                                                <td>Modify the text and terminology used throughout the system.</td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".bd-terminologymodal-modal-lg">Modify</button>                                                                                                     
                                                </td>
                                               </tr>  
                                               <tr>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Cron</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Modify the cron</p></th>
                                                <td>The cron is a task that runs on the system after the defined number of minutes and sets up the defined number of accounts. Used when bulk uploading users to process registrations. Setting these values too high could have a negative impact on the systems performance.</td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".bd-cronmodal-modal-lg">Modify</button>                                                                                                     
                                                </td>
                                               </tr> 
                                               <!-- 26-dec -->
                                                <tr>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Modules</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Module Dates</p></th>
                                                <td>Enabling dates within the module manager tool will require all modules to have start and end date. User will be locked out of their work for a defined period of the time once the end date is reached. Disabled by default.</td>
                                                <% var module_date_checked=''
                                                    if(enabledisablevalue.module_date_enabled){
                                                        module_date_checked=`checked`
                                                    }

                                                %>
                                                <td>
                                                    <label>
                                                        <input class="toggleBtn" type="checkbox" data-name="module_date_enabled" data-toggle="toggle" onchange="setting_enable_disable(this)" <%=module_date_checked %>> </label>                                                                                                             
                                                </td>
                                               </tr>
                                               
                                                <tr class="hide_on_check">
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Modules</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Extension duration</p></th>
                                                <td>The setting define the periods(days) that a user should granted on extension</td>
                                                <td>
                                                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target=".bd-extemsion-duration-modal-lg">Modify</button>                                                                                                           
                                                </td>
                                               </tr>              
                                               <tr>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>System</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Course</p></th>
                                                <td>This setting removes the option of selecting a module on signup/import and adds in the concept of courses, which can be assigned to a student. A course is a pre-defined collection of modules.</td>
                                                <% var checked=''
                                                    if(enabledisablevalue.module_courses_enabled){
                                                        checked=`checked`
                                                    }

                                                %>
                                                
                                                <td>
                                                    <label>
                                                        <input type="checkbox" data-name="module_courses_enabled" data-toggle="toggle" onchange="setting_enable_disable(this)" <%=checked %>> 
                                                    </label>                                                                                                             
                                                </td>
                                               </tr>

                                               <tr>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>System</p></th>
                                                <th scope="row"><p>Teaching Blocks</p></th>
                                                <td>Enable or disable teaching blocks, default is disabled. This setting provides significant changes to how the system operates. Only enable this with advice from Education Host.</td>
                                                <% var teaching_check=''
                                                    if(enabledisablevalue.teaching_block_enabled)
                                                    {
                                                        teaching_check=`checked`
                                                    }

                                                %>
                                                <td>
                                                    <label>
                                                        <input class="toggleBtn" type="checkbox" data-name="teaching_block_enabled" data-toggle="toggle"onchange="setting_enable_disable(this)" <%=teaching_check %>> </label>                                                                                                             
                                                </td>
                                               </tr> 
                                              </tr> 
                                              <% if(enabledisablevalue.teaching_block_enabled) { %>
                                              <tr class="">
                                              <th scope="row"><p>Teaching Block</p></th>
                                              <th scope="row"><p>Marking duration</p></th>
                                              <td>The period (days) a block will be given as standard for it to be marked.</td>
